info.name: growingnn
info.summary: growingnn is a cutting-edge Python package that introduces a dynamic neural network architecture learning algorithm. This innovative approach allows the neural network to adapt its structure during training, optimizing both weights and architecture. Leveraging a Stochastic Gradient Descent-based optimizer and guided Monte Carlo tree search, the package provides a powerful tool for enhancing model performance.
